{"tid":913233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被人慶祝生日果位周同學有冇得民事告佢同學導致佢受傷","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T06:50:51.000Z","uid":45148,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92adc6268d8c31d1e9f0fea7374f8f6f7de4ebf9","tid":913233,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:48:32.000Z","msg":"書都未讀完，就打哂折扣<br />\n講真出來揾食<br />\n第一睇你靚唔靚仔<br />\n第二睇你有冇浸大grad<br />\n第三睇你有冇咩連登仔冇既技能<br />\n<br />\n宜家未出去做野，已經打左個七折<br />\n即係未來收入少左三成<br />\n當一個fresh grad 有15k 1年就18萬<br />\n咁當打40年工 都成720萬<br />\n無左3成 都成200萬<br />\n<br />\n個同學一時疏忽 就令周同學受傷<br />\n有無得民事告下<br />\n拎番小小補償"},{"pid":"25da9ad0e1d834bb33ddad551c6141bb633f26dc","tid":913233,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"刑事都可能入到"},{"pid":"cb97729cade592f4ce0ed07ee3ee9da4be0663a7","tid":913233,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"一定可以"},{"pid":"0a949be493a8a649113d13e5a931c291af9997d7","tid":913233,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a38cd5162013be25604d2df872110a2697a9499","tid":913233,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n因為冇法例"},{"pid":"a1346d4670f932ba44fa9600b5edc3737c805a08","tid":913233,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a38cd5162013be25604d2df872110a2697a9499","tid":913233,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n因為冇法例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"人身傷害"},{"pid":"58f7f766a9bc065e973c8ae1d5216d09afc0db63","tid":913233,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a38cd5162013be25604d2df872110a2697a9499","tid":913233,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"repl